	</A>
the tribe is found east of the Weser; whence Gi<SPAN CLASS="emend">e</SPAN>fers'<!-- Loeb: broken type, "Gi fers" --> conjecture <SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">Ampsivariorum</SPAN>. No certainty can be felt on the point; and it is possible, even, that something is lost before <SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">metanti castra</SPAN>, as it is difficult to suppose that the march from the Ems to the west bank of the Weser could have been passed over without a word.


