onMouseOut="nd();">24</A>
Merivale pointed out that the breadth of the Weser makes the following narrative questionable. Other <SPAN CLASS="whole">over-picturesque</SPAN> touches in Tacitus' sources are Germanicus' dream
	<A HREF="
