onMouseOut="nd();">33</A>
One for each legion. "Critics have superfluously noted that eagles are now rarely if ever seen in those parts, and that their nearest representative, the 'vultur albucillus,' is not gregarious": Furneaux.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
